These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  entrepreneur, architect, manager, bartender, engineer, project-manager, fisherman
1. the architect is in the middle##1
2. the architect is on the left of the manager##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the right of the manager##1
5. the fisherman is on the far left##1
6. the project-manager is on the right of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Job   | fisherman | bartender | engineer | architect | manager | entrepreneur | project-manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, house, techno, disco, dubstep, funk, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of techno##1
5. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of funk##1
6. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | dubstep | techno | funk | disco | house | pop |

