.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, mystery, horror, drama, adventure, western, martial-arts
1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | family | western | horror | martial-arts | mystery | drama |

