3. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the train is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3   |   4    |   5   |   6    |     7      |
| Transport   | van | ship | airplane | train | quad-bike | taxi | helicopter |

