.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-15::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: december, march, october, april, june, january, november
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |  4  |   5    |    6    |      7      |
| Birthday   | march | april | january | june | december | october | november |

